sentences.sentence: FOR more than a decade, physicists running an experiment called DAMA.

sentences.sentence: Hybrid SCPC-DAMA system is especially suitable to thin-route domestic regional and private satellite communication networks.

sentences.sentence: After that a master DAMA controller and three slave DAMA controller and subscriber interface equipments have been accomplished.
